web/app/node_modules/
# web/dist is gitignored but its build outputs are force-added (git add -f)
# after `make web-build`: the Go binary embeds web/dist via go:embed, so the
# committed tree must contain a working build. Always commit the real Vite
# hashed filenames — never copy new builds onto old names (CDNs cache hashed
# assets aggressively; recycled names serve stale bundles).
web/dist/
